85
00:04:13,870 --> 00:04:15,370
He's in there.

86
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:29,050
Lele.

87
00:04:31,610 --> 00:04:33,220
Did you plant all these?

88
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:39,860
It's beautiful.

89
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,180
Lele,

90
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,900
