133
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:31,760
Great.

134
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:33,660
We could use someone
as we're shorthanded.

135
00:06:34,130 --> 00:06:34,690
This way.

136
00:06:34,690 --> 00:06:35,300
All right.

137
00:06:35,610 --> 00:06:36,100
Let's go.

138
