199
00:11:02,850 --> 00:11:03,690
Captain,

200
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:05,620
the child you've

201
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:08,050
been looking for all these years

202
00:11:08,610 --> 00:11:09,380
is me.

