271
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:14,500
Captain,

272
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:16,380
I'm in no rush.

273
00:14:16,730 --> 00:14:18,090
There's still

274
00:14:18,210 --> 00:14:20,090
